The paper focuses on improving the news coverage in Wikipedia entity pages, which involves natural language processing, information retrieval, and knowledge representation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also uses machine learning techniques, which are commonly used in sub-categories such as cs.DL (Machine Learning) and cs.DB (Databases).
